OL,6,FAfter she died in January 2024 at the
OL,7,Fage of 27, her friends and family to
OL,8,Fget the book, called Good Grief, into
OL,9,Fbereavement charities so Rida's words
OL,10,Fcan continue to help people.
OL,12,FRida's sister, Nyla Sheikh, said: "I
OL,13,Fknow Good Grief was really important
OL,14,Fto Rida, and she was so proud of it.
OL,16,F"What I wanted to do was keep her
OL,17,Flegacy going and to keep that good
OL,18,Fwork that she did going ` and there's
OL,19,Fnothing better than her own words."
