OL,6,FFor Nyla, the book has been a source
OL,7,Fof comfort since her sister died.
OL,9,FShe said: "Grief is really hard, and
OL,10,Flosing her is one of the toughest
OL,11,Fthings I've ever been through and one
OL,12,Fof the people I'd love to speak to is
OL,13,Fher, because she helped many people
OL,14,Fwith their journeys with grief.
OL,16,F"Having those words that she
OL,17,Fwrote...that means the world to me
OL,18,Fright now."
