OL,6,FBefore it was a book, Rida's words
OL,7,Fwere originally an award-winning play
OL,8,Fwhich aimed to tackle the ways people
OL,9,Fdeal with the loss of a loved one
OL,10,Fthrough comedy.
OL,12,FTheatre Company Ugly Bucket produced
OL,13,Fthe play, and approached Rida to ask
OL,14,Fif she would share her story of losing
OL,15,Fboth of her parents when she was a
OL,16,Fchild.
