OL,3,CLoving nurse's legacy lives on in book
OL,4,Cabout grief
OL,6,FThe Co-Artistic Director of Ugly
OL,7,FBucket, Grace Gallagher, said: "Rida
OL,8,Fwas someone who, in her life had
OL,9,Fexperienced a lot of grief, and she
OL,10,Fwas really passionate about talking
OL,11,Fabout it more and opening up that
OL,12,Fconversation.
OL,14,F"I think that Rida was so important to
OL,15,FGood Grief because she became the
OL,16,Flight in the show, in the darkness."
OL,18,FThe play told Rida's story of learning
OL,19,Fto live with her grief, alongside
OL,20,Fother people who had lost loved ones.
